{{Main|Mirador de la Flor}}
({{lang-en|Lookout of the Flower}}) also known as '''Selena's seawall''',<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tripadvisor.co.nz/Attraction_Review-g60927-d239600-Reviews-Mirador_del_Flor_Selena_s_Seawall_Statue-Corpus_Christi_Texas.html|title=Mirador del Flor / Selena's Seawall Statue|work=[[TripAdvisor]]|accessdate=October 25, 2017}}</ref> is Selena's own life-size [[bronze sculpture|bronze statue]] [[monument]] in [[Corpus Christi, Texas]] sculpted by [[H. W. Tatum|H.W. "Buddy" Tatum]] and unveiled in 1997.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://periodicosintesis.com.mx/noticias/59337/Selena-vive-en-sus-canciones|title=Selena vive en sus canciones|last=de la Fuente|first=Tamaño|date=30 March 2010|work=Sintesis|language=Spanish|accessdate=31 March 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722224329/http://periodicosintesis.com.mx/noticias/59337/Selena-vive-en-sus-canciones|archivedate=July 22, 2011|df=mdy-all}}</ref> About 30,000 people from around the world visit this monument every year.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.caller.com/news/2005/apr/01/dedicated-fans-tour-selena-related-sites/|title=Dedicated fans tour Selena-related sites Many spend 10th anniversary of her death at mirador|last=Fernandez|first=Icess|date=1 April 2005|work=[[Corpus Christi Caller-Times]]|accessdate=31 March 2010}}</ref>

